Dear Student,

The Higher Education Commission of Pakistan (HEC) is pleased to announce
the opening of applications for the HEC Need-Based Scholarship Programme
2026-27. This scholarship is designed to support financially deserving
students enrolled in HEC-recognized universities.

Scholarship Details:
- Coverage: Full tuition fee waiver + PKR 3,000/month stipend
- Number of Slots: 5,000 students nationwide
- Eligible Programs: Bachelor's (Semester 1-8), Master's (Semester 1-4)

Eligibility Criteria:
- Currently enrolled in HEC-recognized university
- CGPA of 2.5 or above (on a 4.0 scale)
- Family income less than PKR 45,000/month
- No other active scholarship

Required Documents:
1. Income certificate from Union Council / NADRA
2. Current semester enrollment certificate
3. Official university transcript
4. CNIC copy (student + parents)
5. Last utility bill of residence

Application Deadline: May 10, 2026

Apply Online: https://hec.gov.pk/scholarships/need-based-2026
FAQs: https://hec.gov.pk/scholarships/faq

For assistance, contact: nbscholarship@hec.gov.pk | 051-111-119-432

